<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Successful</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #28a745; /* Green background */
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 100px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #28a745;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit; /* Ensure the link color matches the button text */
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #f1f1f1; /* Light hover effect for the button */
        }
    </style>
     
</head>
<body style="background-color: #28a745;">

<h1>Order Placed Successfully !</h1>
<button><a href="/shop">Continue Shopping</a></button>

</body>
</html>
